high_descs: Turn right and then turn to your left right away so you are facing the bread
Pick up a spoon off of the kitchen counter
Move to your right and face the microwave
Open the microwave and put the spoon in to the cup
Pick up the cup with the spoon it in and close the microwave
Turn left three times so that you are facing the kitchen counter with your back to the fridge
Place the cup on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Take a step right.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Place the spoon in the gold cup in the microwave.
Pick up the cup
Walk left and around the kitchen island to the part facing the fridge.
Place the cup on the kitchen island to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a spoon in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, then turn left to base the counter with the bread on it.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, behind the bread.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the spoon in the cup in the microwave.
Pick up the cup with the spoon in it.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, step forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Put the cup with the spoon in it on the kitchen island, to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it on the kitchen island.
